Email Etiquette Checklist:-

Here is a quick checklist that you can follow before sending any email:
 Basic Structure
✔ Clear subject line
✔ Proper greeting
✔ Clear and concise message
✔ Proper closing
 Writing Style
✔ Write in a formal and respectful manner
✔ Avoid using slang
✔ Use simple and clear sentences
✔ Grammar and spell check
 Professional Tone
✔ Use polite language
✔ Avoid coming across as demanding
✔ To the point
 Formatting
✔ Use paragraphs
✔ Avoid using too many emojis
✔ Proper spacing and alignment
 Before Sending
✔ Read once
✔ Check the email ID
✔ Attach files if necessary
